research_municipality_step.notes: The position of Mayor for Seadrift city, TX is currently vacant, with an election scheduled for May 2, 2026. One Alderman position is also vacant due to a resignation in January 2026, and a special election will be held on May 2, 2026, to fill it. Alysa Jarvis serves as Mayor Pro Tem.
